Brand new 12 volt 200 mm flywheel (stock) $75.00 dollars outright (add 10
dollars to drill for 8 dowel). I am a SCAT dealer and have had discussions
with them about making stock weight flywheels and they are thinking about
it. SCAT is also in the process of making FORGED 69 mm counterweighted
cranks to compliment there cast 69 mm CW cranks. Should be available in
January.

